  * iPod support is back. Added versioned build-dep on libgpod-dev (>=0.4.2).
    (Closes: #409985)
  * Add patch to add the "Queue Track" functionality to the Amarok DCOP API:
    queuemedia.patch. Patch by Isaac Clerencia <isaac@debian.org>
